  ${
    $d x y U $.
    hilnorm.5 $e |- ~H = ( BaseSet ` U ) $.
    hilnorm.2 $e |- .ih = ( .i ` U ) $.
    hilnorm.9 $e |- U e. NrmCVec $.
    $( Hilbert space norm in terms of vector space norm. $)
    hilnormi $p |- normh = ( norm ` U ) $=
      ( vx vy cv chil wcel cnm cfv wceq wa copab csp co csqr cno cnv eqid ipnm
