  ${
    hilhh.1 $e |- ~H = ( BaseSet ` U ) $.
    hilhh.2 $e |- +h = ( +v ` U ) $.
    hilhh.3 $e |- .h = ( .s ` U ) $.
    hilhh.5 $e |- .ih = ( .i ` U ) $.
    hilhh.9 $e |- U e. NrmCVec $.
    $( Deduce the structure of Hilbert space from its components. $)
    hilhhi $p |- U = <. <. +h , .h >. , normh >. $=
      ( cnv wcel cva csm cop cno wceq hilnormi nvop ax-mp ) AGHAIJKLKMFJAILCDAB
