  ${
    $d k v w x y z U $.
    hhnv.1 $e |- U = <. <. +h , .h >. , normh >. $.
    $( Hilbert space is a normed complex vector space. $)
    hhnv $p |- U e. NrmCVec $=
      ( vx vy csm cva cno chil c0v cabl wcel cgr hilabl ablogrpo ax-mp cxp
